data.description: Step into a contemporary gem in the heart of North Raleigh - this like new townhome seamlessly combines sophistication with practicality. Spread across three stories, this residence offers a dynamic living experience for those seeking modern comfort and style. The open-concept design welcomes you into a light-filled living area, situated on the 2nd floor, sets the stage for gatherings and relaxation. It effortlessly connects to a gourmet kitchen adorned with high-end appliances, granite countertops, and a huge island - a haven for culinary enthusiasts.  Step out of the kitchen onto your private deck, an ideal space for outdoor dining or quiet moments in the fresh air. Meticulously landscaped surroundings create a serene backdrop for outdoor activities or gatherings with friends.  Ascending the staircase, discover three bedrooms on the upper levels. The owner's suite, a private retreat on the top floor, boasts a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bath. The additional bedrooms accommodate the needs of a growing family or provide space for a home office. The convenience of an attached one-car garage cannot be overstated, providing secure parking and additional storage space. It's the perfect complement to the townhome's modern lifestyle. Situated in a sought-after North Raleigh neighborhood, this townhome is surrounded by an array of amenities. From nearby parks and schools to shopping centers and restaurants, everything you need is within easy reach. Commuting is a breeze with quick access to major highways, making Raleigh's downtown and beyond easily accessible.  Elevate your lifestyle with this contemporary townhome - where modern design meets practicality. Your dream home awaits in Raleigh, NC!
